| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2335 — Recovery Inhibition (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: fc57e799-b8fc-50ee-84f3-59a59f266e41"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
